column_.text_:
Make haste! The castle's undercroft should be just down this
corridor!

Man, those poor Seedhollow guards. They didn't sign up for
this...

Lilith... She must be stopped before her corruption spreads
further!
Shall we continue on? This skydom isn't going to save itself.
It won't open. Is there a way around?
Darn, this path was a bust. Let's try find another way in.
Don't tell me you're getting cold feet now.

We can't turn back. Get your head in the game, and let's
move on.
My, my. Running from duty? How unlike you.
Please... Don't abandon these people.
Going back ain't gonna help nobody! Forward march!
Gah! We found trouble!

I thought we cleared out this area... Get outta here or face the
Silver Wolf Corps!

You idiot, it's that crew! Lady Lilith will reward us
generously for their heads!

We got too much on the line to back down now! Give 'em
heck, bud!

We got too much on the line to back down now! Give 'em
heck, bud!
If fighting is the only way through, then so be it! To arms!
The ol' direct assault, eh? I can get behind that!
You guys had a chance to back down! Just remember that!

You people have gone too far! You're not gonna Angra
Man-ize our Lyria, you hear me!

No time for civil conversation, it seems. Let them taste your
thorns!

They just never let us pass, do they? C'mon, Geegee! Let's
get 'em!
This battle will be fierce! But we shall prevail!

Come on, guys. Why can't we ever settle things with a good
ol' fashioned chat?

Hah. Is this rabble all Avia could muster? They are no more
soldiers than their leader is a prophet.
Shatter their lines! Into the fray!
Break their ranks! We shall emerge victorious!

Those fellars don't look friendly. But they'll soon find out
who's the salmon and who's the bear.

The untempered mind is prey to manipulation... Know your
folly!

You attempt to overwhelm with numbers alone! But the
mighty ox does not bow before a swarm of flies!
Well, who do we have here? More dorks for me to stomp!

Bring your numbers. You will never have enough to match
our strength!

What, you think you can stall us with such a pathetic force?
Morons.
Hmph. Only one way through.

Don't back down! We have the power of the primeval gods on
our side!

Primeval gods, huh? Amazing how that term persists, six
hundred years after I first formed Avia.

Lilith and I were working on our experiment, studying the
effects of skydweller emotions—such as faith—on primal
beasts.

But she twisted the convictions of the masses, reshaping
them as building blocks for this paramilitaristic cult.

Lady Lilith will guide us to the promised land! We do not fear
death!
Inquisitor Rook's troop will be here soon! Hold on till then!

The Church finds you in defiance of Our Lady's grand
message! Face your penance!

Now we have to deal with full-on battleships? This is not in
my job description!

We don't have time to repel all of them! Stopping Lilith
comes first!
Wait, Rolan. Weren't you the one who sealed Angra Mainyu?
Indeed. Five hundred years ago...

You couldn't find a better location? For skies' sake, putting a
primal like that under a damn metropolis!

Forgive me. It was the height of the War, and I needed a
place inaccessible to an Astral like Lilith.

So you chose an enemy stronghold. Not exactly a 
conventional plan, but effective nonetheless.

How dare you fabricate these lies about Lady Lilith's Astral
origins! You will learn to stay your tongues, interlopers!
Finally broke through 'em. Onward and downward?

These soldiers are not to blame for Lilith's machinations, and
yet they're the ones paying the ultimate price...
A little debris won't stop us. Allow me.

You can fight, you can clear rubble... Think you can clean an
airship?
What's the pay like? Shall we talk price?
Quickly. The undercroft should be close.
Gah! Hit the deck!
Warship cannons! These Avia jerks do not play fair!

We can take refuge in the cellars below! There's no way their
fusillade will reach us down there!

I just hope they stop firing completely! This castle's too pretty
to be destroyed!

Gonna take half a miracle to bring down that carrier. So, do
we run or...

Hmm, judging from the position of this tower... The terrace
leading to the court should be close! Let's head there!

Now we face the interlopers who routed Rook and his men!
For Lady Lilith!
For Lady Lilith!
Again? We're just gonna steamroll them anyway!

If we stand firm, they will back down. Don't give them an
inch!

Man, these guys don't know when to quit! Unfortunately for
them, neither do I!
Ugh, can't you people take a hint? We're sick of you!

Normally I like devotion in my mercs, but you punks take it
too far.
We're outnumbered. Don't let them surround us!

Doesn't matter how persistent you are. I'll whip you silly
every time!

Seems like combat is our only choice... Everyone, break
through their lines!

I hate picking on the little guy, but you jerks are really chafing
my chaps!

Like so many moths... Too witless to understand the peril of
the flames.

Zealots. They won't back down without a strong show of
force.

You shall let us pass! Lest you face the wrath of mighty
Lumiel!

Takes a bunch of small fry to keep the whole school
a-swimmin'! Hyuk-hyuk, now let's dismiss this class!

This is your last chance to change your fate... Let us through,
or answer to my blade!

Battle just whets my appetite for more battle... Come! Let us
feast!

Wow, guess some people can't help but play with fire. Let's
give 'em what they want, Arvess!
I was hoping it wouldn't come to this, but you give me choice.

You dopes must have only a handful of brain cells between
you. Why else would you stand in my way?
You're making the wrong choice, soldiers!

You foul interlopers! We will not let you stand in the way of
our glorious mission!

Oh, you've got to be kidding me! Do you even know what
Lilith is planning to do?

How dare you question Our Lady! She will guide us to
salvation, to Estalucia!
No! You're wrong!

She would swallow this whole skydom to see her selfish
ambitions fulfilled! You included!
Just as... Just as she did fifteen years ago in Dahli!

If you aim to fill my head with deceit, it will not work! You
will pay for making a mockery of Lady Lilith!

They would die before doubting Lilith? She has them utterly
bewitched!

Maybe now's not the best time for conversion. Let's save the
de-brainwashing till after the fighting shall we?

You promise these skydwellers salvation while ushering
them toward doom... Lilith, you are a fiend.
Yeah! And don't even think about coming back!
Now then, we better keep moving.

While I normally think that patience is the best virtue, maybe
we should pick up the pace.

Looks like a dead end. I saw some stairs heading down back
at that door, though.
Ah, perfect! That should lead us to the terrace!
Uh-oh! Company!

In the name of Silver Wolf Corps, we will stop your
blasphemy here and now!

...And it would be a lot easier, if those damned Sword Veil
mages were at their posts! Why haven't they come yet?!

General Maglielle pulled 'em back! Said they were worn out
from Dahli!

Hah! Are they a bunch of babies? General Gallanza would
never let us have nap time!
Uh-wah!
Now they have more toys to harass us with. Peachy!

They've really deployed it, the tayu'itar! But it should still be
in the research phase...

The multiple legs allow for maximum stability and
maneuverability. It has high firepower and horsepower, and a
certain je ne sais quoi.
We get it, you dork! How do we blow it up?

Heh, sorry... Just like you blow anything else up? Though
maybe we could try to salvage it... Aheh...
It's just a big hunk of scrap! Show it we mean business!
We can't let it wreak anymore havoc! Come on, everyone!

Avia has weapons out the you-know-what, but that doesn't
mean we'll give up!

What do you get when you combine a tank with magic? I'll
give you a hint: Kaboom!

You guys brought a tank to fight an engineer? I could
disassemble this thing with my eyes closed!

I can feel a disorienting force... It's bolstering this weapon!
Careful, everyone!

It's reinforced with metal... We might have to rethink our
battle plan, team.

I prefer mechanical foes. It means neither pity nor mercy will
dull my fangs!

Holy nuggets, this thing is sa-weet! Too bad you guys wanna
hurt people with it...

Vassals, behind me. Fire is more a match for machinery than
flesh or steel.

Its movements are straightforward, inorganic. This should be
simple.

A clod of iron is no match for a will of diamond! Victory shall
be ours!

Theeeere's a hole in the log, in the frog, in the crusader, in
the tank, in the bottom of the castle...

When brandished for war, even the most beautiful blade
blackens the soul... But I shall purge you!
Dishonorable garbage!
Fat chance stopping me with a pile of nuts and bolts!
These machines have a sizable arsenal. Watch my back.

An interesting design, for a weaponized automaton. Perhaps
I should look into the technological advances of this skydom.
Good luck. I know all about these machines.

This thing has a head harder than Rackam's! But he doesn't
move like the wind!

Its legs should be lightly armored compared to the core!
That's where we should focus our fire!

Look! The actuators in its limbs are beginning to buckle! The
pressure differential should result in—
Rolan! None of us speak nerd! What do you mean?
Heh, sorry! Our assault is working!
Perfect!

Look at its sluggish maneuvers! One more push, and we'll
have it out of commission!
It stopped moving! Hit it with everything you've got!

It reactivated?! How did it switch to its power reserves so
quickly?
Why are its legs glowing, Rolan? What's it gonna do?

Exposing its ether frame? That could only mean... Watch out!
It's preparing to fire a huge blast!

Let's scrap this thing before it shoots us straight to kingdom
come!
Knock its legs out! That should do the trick!
It's too late! Get as much distance as you can!
Son of a... This damn robospider plays dirty!

Yep, that was too close for comfort. Gotta take out those
legs before it can pull that again.

Look! Its head is exposed! Attack it before we miss our
chance!

Not often you see sensor malfunctions like this. Caused by a
short circuit within the mainframe perhaps. Or maybe—

Again? Who cares about all that? We just need to destroy it,
right?
Ah, sorry! Yes, that's the plan!
Ahh, the family that slays together, stays together.
Did it change its weaponry? Everyone, be on guard!

It's switched artillery again! Watch out for changes in its
attack patterns!
Ngh, that's not good!

We won't be able to lay a finger on it while its boosters are
active! Focus on evasion for now!

Easy enough for you to say! Do you see it dashing around
everywhere?

This model of tayu'itar expends tons of energy while
boosting! It shouldn't last much longer!
If only we could explain it to death...
Yeah! We beat the screws outta that robo!

Well done! And what a relief we didn't completely destroy
such a fine specimen.

Hold on... Hear that humming? I don't think we're out of the
woods yet!
Now we have to fight two of 'em?
Allow me!
Haaaa...
Don't mind if I recruit a little help!

Its core seems undamaged... I could use it to fight off the
others!

Did you really just hop up on that thing? Do you even have a
license?

Where we're going, we have no need for licenses! It'll be a
cinch to cover you!
Why does Rolan always get weirder around new machines?
Yeah, I don't like that twinkle in his eye...

Oh, come now! Why must you criticize me mid-battle! Can't
we focus?

Prepare all cannons! We have to give our reinforcement
tayu'itar time to come online!

Hah, hoping to bombard us? They should know that won't
leave a scratch on this puppy!
More cannonfire! Hold steady, tayu'itar!
Yeah! It's working!
Suck on that, Avia punks!

How the hell is he getting it to react like that? Feels like it's
alive!
You... you insolent heathen!
Damn it, we're done for if we don't take him out!

Two against one isn't very fair odds. Perhaps you should call
in a third?

Ah, this beaut never seems to run out of munitions. If only
we could apply such revolutionary technology for society's
benefit!

I've shot past the tayu'itar's maximum output! I'll fire on the
enemy ship while it's still operational!

Wouldn't it be nice if, I don't know, they stopped firing on us
already!

Considering the elevation angle, muzzle velocity... Yes, I think
I can hit them!
Hell yeah! One down, one to go!
We've destroyed them both! Well done, team!
Can't you blast those ships out of the sky?

Now for the battleship! Hit 'em with their own medicine,
Rolan!
You got 'em! I could kiss you, Rolan!
Hang on! I'll start an emergency reboot!

Showin' off the Fix in Mr. Fix It, eh! We oughta hire you full
time!
Just a moment! I'll get it humming again!
I don't see any major damage... It should still work!
Looks like the coast is clear for now!
Tayu'itar... Good night, sweet prince. You will be missed.
More rubble, is it? Never fear, I'll have it removed posthaste!

Now, there should be an entrance to the undercroft from the
front of the court! Let's hurry!

What a splendid marvel of engineering. Hopefully one day it
will be used for something other than a weapon.
This tea is simply to die for.
There's no better appetizer to a banquet of blood.
Now then...
Hmph... I knew you'd be back for more.

In the name of the Sword Veil Fellowship... I shan't let you
take another step.
Let's have a clean...
Deathmatch!
Who cares about these bozos? You stick it to 'em, pal!
Who cares about these bozos? You stick it to 'em, pal!
I accept your challenge! Let us finish this!

I'm getting real tired of seeing your ugly mugs. Let's make
this quick.

You idiots want a real deathmatch, huh? Fine, you've got
one!

We're your main course? Then how about an asskicking for
dessert?

Two enemy generals at the same time? Hah. Now it's a
party.
Let's show them what real teamwork looks like!

Let this be an honorable match between standard-bearers.
You face the captain of the White Dragons himself!

A deathmatch? Sounds serious... In which case, you face the
vice captain of the White Dragons himself!

You fight for the elation; I fight because I must... That is why
you will never triumph!

They might've strayed from the right path, but they are still
powerful soldiers with conviction. Do not underestimate
them!

O distinguished warriors, I accept your challenge! Let us have
a most noble fight!

Hmm... Got some gumption, do ya? Fine. I know a trick or
two that might end this swiftly!

Even the mighty mountain cannot stop the wandering wind...
Face me!

A deathmatch? You honor me! This will be a fine test of the
Eternal Rage Style!
Bring it, chumps! Let's see what the odd couple can do!
I accept your challenge. Now perish.

There's no reason I should waste my time on either of you
peabrains. But I could blow off a little steam! Let's do this!

How long has it been since either of you has won a match
against me? Today won't be any different!

I've been waiting for this! A deathmatch befitting Avia's two
strongest generals!

As you can see, my boorish compatriot is in need of some
entertainment. Do not disappoint us.

I knew Avia's elite would be strong, but these two take it to a
whole different level!

You flatter us, sir. May we have the honor of knowing your
name before we destroy you?

Strange etiquette... But I'm just a nobody from a far away
island.

Exactly what a master fighter would say! You cannot hide the
depth of your skill from me, a connoisseur of strength!

Mwahaha! I knew there was more to you! Show me what
else you can do!

Oh dear, look what you've done. General Gallanza is
unstoppable once riled up.

Had enough yet? Or do you freaks get your kicks from
fighting a losing battle?
Do not assume you have won the war yet, skyfarer.
Or do! Haha, that pride will be your downfall!
Mwahaha! More! Show me more of that power!
Hyah! Ready for the next round!
Ngh! How uncouth!
The interlude is over. Shall we finish this charade?
By sword!
By spear!
Madness consume you!
They're attacking in tandem!

Linking together was your parlor trick, was it not? I think
we've rather perfected it!

Yes! Legends will be told of the mighty "Gallanza
Extravaganza!"
Excuse me, the what? I deserve credit too!
The veil...
Sends its regards!
Gallanza!
Maglielle?
Link Especiál!

Now we're getting to the good part! Can you feel the passion
burning?!

No, but I feel my ears bleeding! You shout more than anyone
we've ever fought!
Now then, I think it's about time I seized my rightful victory!
Careful, everyone! He's going to attempt something reckless!
Weapons of yore, give me strength!

She's created a whirlwind of blades! How do we evade them
all!

Don't you see? We will not fall! We have too much on the
line!

Then that goes double for us! We won't abandon Lyria, or
the Sky Realm!
The wolf bears his fangs!
Storming Death!
Impressed?
You foul cretins!
There is nowhere to hide!
The veil reveals her sword!
Symphony Superiór!
Swords everywhere! What do we do?
Defend yourself as best you can! We mustn't lose hope!

The honor of my kinfolk is on the line! My blades will find you
no matter what!
C'mon! Show 'em what we got!
Indeed... Just as we planned...
Look to the stars! Hah!
They shall guide us!
To providence we sail!
Silver Veil Storm!
Aaargh! I can't get a bead on them!

It's amazing. They've managed to combine might and skill in
perfect harmony.
Un, deux, trois... Strike now!
Thought you'd never ask!
One more time! Hah!
Let's not leave them wanting...
Now for the encore!
Silver Veil Storm!

Here comes another powerful technique! Stay focused and
do not falter!
General Gallanza, if you please!
Pack it up! This show's over!
Heh, not bad, skyfarers. Not bad.
General Gallanza? Bested by hooligans?

Do you see now, Maglielle? You have no hope of defeating
us. Throw down your weapons.

No... I will use every fiber of my magic to ensure you never
leave this hall!
I respect the determination, but you've lost your mind, lady!
I cannot fail! There's too much at stake!
Stars! Please, guide us...
I mustn't fall... The Veil...
You sleep tight, Maggie. I'll handle the rest.
Man, can't you just quit? We're all clearly worn out here!

A wolf doesn't scamper off with his tail between his legs.
Now fight me, cowards!

Yeah, yeah, I figured this is how it would go. Not really a
deathmatch without the "death" part, is it?
Oooh-ho-ho! Now this is exciting! Lay it all on the line!
Gahaha... What an amazing day...
Good... I regret nothing...
My lady?

I know well the lunacy of my position, to be making demands
of you.

But please, the Sword Veil are my family. If you can, find it in
your heart to spare them.
Take me.

I staked my life on this deathmatch. Now come claim your
hard-earned spoils!
Look, we just wanna get through here without trouble.

As long as you stay outta our way, we got no reason to fight
anymore. Deal?
There's no time to waste.
Forgive my failure, Lady Lilith...
Complete and utter defeat. They might actually pull it off...

Those two freaks were crazy. Crazy strong, I mean. I hope
we've seen the last of them.

They were masters of their respective arts. Why do they
follow Lilith?

Even great warriors may find themselves prey to hard times.
Salvation, no matter how false, seems an alluring prize.

And well... Some Astrals have a certain charm, which can
prove intoxicating to many skyfarers.

They've got all the nasty tricks... But what about Lilith's 
son? He an Astral too?

Mercifully, no. He's a skydweller, same as you. As far as I 
can tell, Lilith took him in as a child.

Not every day you hear about an Astral adopting a regular 
Joe. Whatever's going on here, it don't sit right with me.
It seems we've reached a dead end.
Not to worry! There's another path this way.
Fix It Dude should know the way forward! Let's ask!
Here we are. Would you all please stand back?

Up ahead is the altar where Angra Mainyu lies sealed. We will
no doubt find Lilith there already.

A special ward warps time and space around Angra, making
physical contact impossible. Let us hope Lilith has not
breached it yet.

We have only one shot at victory. I will strike the moment
she calls for Angra.
So when it gets its fuel, blast the engine? Yep, that'll do it!
Okay, people, look alive! This one's for Lyria!
Oh no, is that...
Lyria! Let's move!
Aah... It's been so long...

Finally the dawning of salvation is upon us. The path will
soon open.
Oh!
I wasn't expecting to see them again.
That's enough! Lyria's coming back with us!
Is that so?
Id.
You're all talk!
What happened to that stuff about protectin' Lyria?
You know what to do.
Help me, please...
It can't be... Astraeus?
It's been a while, Director.
Of... course...
This was all... your doing...
Mother!
Id. Don't worry about me.
Just focus on them.
I've been waiting for you to return and cast open a gate.
So I can destroy Angra Mainyu!
Stay out of our way!
What's the big idea! We don't have time to mess with you!
Leave now.

Look around! Do you honestly believe Lyria deserves any of
this?
I believe in Mother's plan.
If you won't let us pass, we'll take you out! You big dummy!
Fine! Then we shall prove your beliefs false!

Well, looks like we're at an impasse. Luckily that's where I
do my best target practice!

Lilith has been using Lyria like a tool! Even if she is your
mom, how can you trust someone like that?

I know you don't want to betray the woman who raised you.
But you need to see reason, kid.
You will return Lyria to us. My thorns insist.

I can't fault you for standing by your beliefs. But that doesn't
mean we'll back down either!

I hoped we would come to an understanding. Now I see that
was mere wishful thinking!

And here I thought you seemed like a reasonable guy. You
sure had me fooled. ...Jerk.

I understand how you feel... But you cannot allow filial love to
cloud your judgement!

I see negotiation fails us. Then we settle our differences by
way of combat!

How unfortunate that you did not come to your senses! We
shall see Lyria returned regardless!

Oh, sonny. I can tell by the way your sword's droopin' that
you've got a lot on your heart. Come, let's clear the air!

One does not reason with faith... Yet we cannot abandon our
friend!

Words have failed us. Let us settle this through the noble art
of fisticuffs!

Open your eyes, man... Guess we'll do this the old-fashioned
way!

Take a look at my scythe. Sure you don't want to talk this out
instead?

Oooh, look at all those secrets inside you... I'll reveal every
single one!

I knew this path was wrong... And yet, I could not turn away
from Mother...
Nrgh... Fair enough.

You have caused this crew untold agony! But this time will
be different!
How have they become this much stronger?!

You picked the wrong crew to mess with, pal! Weird cult or
ancient gods, we always find a way to push through!
I've seen enough!
I will destroy you!

Where is he getting this kind of power? The sheer
concentration of magic is extraordinary!

I've always thought he was inhumanly strong, but inhuman
magic to boot? What the heck is he?!
Well... His counters are fearsome.

Yep, let's not make that mistake again. Lay off the attacks
while he's in that stance.

He rushes forward with furious speed... But he should still
have a weakness.

He's a monster when he's angry, but you can't cover all your
bases when you move like a bat outta hell.
Reginleiv!
Reginleiv!
You think you can save Lyria?
What a fool.
All right.
Enough! This ends now!
Awaken...
Your dawn has arrived!
Become my power!
Holy cow! What's happening to him?
Awaken...
Your dawn has arrived!
Become my power!
Holy cow! What's happening to him?

The waves of power coursing through him... It's unlike any
monster or primal beast I know.

Maybe Lilith pumped him full of destructo-juice? I'd believe
anything at this point!
That purple flame can't be good! You better put it out quick!

A flame that corrupts instead of burns? How is that
possible? Can we extinguish it?
Hey, are you all right?!
His attacks activate that weird fire! We have to be careful!
Our offensive is clearly having an effect! Keep it up, everyone!

Now's our chance! He shouldn't be able to access those
corrupt powers for awhile!
He's back on his feet! And madder than ever!
Gaaah! He's at it again!

If we blindly attack him, he'll counter with twice the force.
We need to choose our openings carefully!

That momentum is double-edged sword. We'll have a chance
to strike as soon as he stops charging.

I know how to take him down! Look for the gap right after
his rushing attack—that's when we strike!
Must protect...

What a terrifying torrent of mana... He filled this entire room
in an instant!
Yep, that speed is a serious problem!

Well he can't just dash around all day, can he? We have to
find his weak spot!
Save her...
This is not what Lyria would want! Why do you fight us, Id?!
Lyria! Graaawr!

He's gone off the rails! Pretty soon he'll cause this whole
basement to collapse!

I'm too young to be entombed beneath a castle! We gotta
beat him quick!
I'm not through...
Is he... Is he actually down?
Let's just get to Lyria.
Come on... We're so close.
Lyria!
Hi, everyone...
You came to get me...
Look up!
Farewell. Enjoy your tomb.
Not if I...
...kill you first!
Try it!
All of you—run! Get away from here while you still can!

Worrying about the rain while drowning in the sea? You
always were such a careless one.
Urgh!
Cast open...
Gates to worlds beyond—Angra Mainyu!
I won't... Let you do this!
Rolan, no!
Did he just...
He's gone...
Damn... Guess we're next! Get ready!
Estalucia is the first stop on my return to the Astral Realm.
All who dare obstruct me shall perish into nothing.
Angra Mainyu... The primal beast who distorts space itself...

I can't believe it overpowered Rolan so easily. This fight's
going to get desperate. Stay vigilant.

You skydwellers are autumn leaves, and I am the winter of
your discontent. My coming is your death.

Even Astraeus was no match for me. I could likely blow you
over with a single breath.

Why you... That's it! We won't let you get away with your
nasty schemes! Put up your dukes!
That's right!

Now that we have Lyria back, we can cut loose! Let 'em
have it!

Lyria... I'm so glad you're safe. Now. To punish this evil
woman who abducted you!

I'm used to playing it by ear, and my ears are telling me to
pull out the big guns!

We've come too far to lose to a dumb kidnapper! Lyria, back
us up, okay?

We'll finish up our emotional reunion later! First comes
beatin' these punks!
The atmosphere feels twisted. It, it's overwhelming.

Your days of exploiting the Sky Realm are over! Any last
words?

We must hold this position, even if it spells our doom! Angra
Mainyu cannot be allowed to escape!
Step one: defeat the bad guys! Step two: save the world!
Do not be daunted, my vassals! On me!

I know that facing the unknown is frightening, but we'll be all
right. Just stay close and follow my lead!
I swear on this holy blade, I shall see evil vanquished!
